  "title": "EVENTSCREW/SALES ASSOCIATE",
  "description": "<p>We’re an <strong>outsourced sales and marketing team</strong> partnering with reputable brands across multiple industries—<strong>telco, broadband, lifestyle products, and charitable organisations</strong>.</p><p>Our role is simple: <strong>bring brands to life</strong> by engaging customers directly, anywhere the action is.</p><p>This is a <strong>consumer-facing role</strong> where you work with a large market and high footfall. The more people you engage, the greater your impact—and the better your results.</p><p>If you enjoy starting conversations, meeting new people, and working with a fun, motivated team, you’ll fit right in.</p><h2>Your Mission</h2><ul><li><p>Engage customers <strong>face-to-face</strong> and represent brand campaigns professionally</p></li><li><p>Create positive, memorable experiences that build trust</p></li><li><p>Guide customers toward solutions that genuinely fit their needs</p></li><li><p>Work with a high-energy team to achieve targets together</p></li></ul><h2>What We’re Looking For</h2><ul><li><p>Energetic, outgoing, and curious individuals</p></li><li><p>Comfortable speaking to new people</p></li><li><p><strong>No experience required</strong> — full training and coaching provided</p></li></ul><h2>Why You’ll Love It</h2><ul><li><p><strong>Attractive commission and incentive structure</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Fast progression</strong> for strong performers</p></li><li><p>Build real confidence, communication, and presentation skills</p></li><li><p>Supportive, youthful, and performance-driven team culture</p></li></ul><p>If you want, I can:</p><ul><li><p>Make this <strong>shorter and more hype-driven</strong></p></li><li><p>Adapt it for <strong>Telegram, Instagram, or job portals</strong></p></li><li><p>Add a <strong>strong call-to-action</strong> to boost applications</p></li></ul>",
